pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Vital Energy 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine as an adaptogen and to support energy levels and vitality.

Wanderlust Vital Energy is a consciously created blend of plant actives. Siberian Ginseng is traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine as an adaptogen and to support energy levels, vitality and immune system health. Ashwagandha is traditionally used in Ayurvedic Medicine as a rejuvenating tonic, to relieve nervous tension and help the body adapt to stress.

Size: 60 Capsules

Warnings

Contains phenylalanine (naturally occurring in organic spirulina).

Talk to an Ayurvedic practitioner/health professional if you are unsure if this medicine is right for you.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:
Eleutherococcus senticosus (Siberian Ginseng) root ext. dry cone, 150 mg Derived from dry------------1.5g
Withania somnifera (Ashwagandha) root ext. dry cone . 300 mg
Derived from dry------------1.5g
Arthrospira platensis powder (Organic Spirulina) 100 mg

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Take two capsules daily or as directed by your healthcare practitioner.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry
place. Do not use if cap seal or
inner seal is missing or broken.
